data.title: About: Kathryn Greiner
data.meta_description: Kathryn Therese Greiner AO (born 1946) is an Australian politician and social advocate. She is a former Alderman of the City of Sydney 1995–2004. She is separated from Nick Greiner, a former Premier of New South Wales.

dbo:abstract

كاثرين غرينير (بالإنجليزية: Kathryn Greiner)‏ هي عاملة إجتماعية أسترالية، ولدت في 1946. (ar)

Kathryn Therese Greiner AO (born 1946) is an Australian politician and social advocate. She is a former Alderman of the City of Sydney 1995–2004. She is separated from Nick Greiner, a former Premier of New South Wales. (en)
